Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: Products.UserField
Version: 3.0
Summary: Archetypes Field dealing with Plone Users and assign local roles.
Home-page: https://svn.plone.org/svn/archetypes/MoreFieldsAndWidgets/UserField
Author: BlueDynamics Alliance
Author-email: dev@bluedynamics.com
License: BSD
Description: =========
        UserField
        =========
        
        -------
        Purpose
        -------
        
        UserField is an Archetypes field with some functionality to 
        
        * store user and/or group ids, 
        
        * set local roles based on the selection, 
        
        * group limitation. 
        
        and some more.
        
